  "text": "3.1.3.2 Multi-Oriented Text: Another distinction from general text detection is that text detection is rotationsensitive and skewed text are common in real-world, while using traditional axis-aligned prediction boxes would incorporate noisy background that would affect the performance of the following text recognition module. Several methods have been proposed to adapt to it [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] , [CITATION_4] , [CITATION_5] , [CITATION_6] , [CITATION_7] , [CITATION_8] [CITATION_9] .",
